name: Historical landings for the lagoon of Venice (Italy) between 1945 and 2001
description: The dataset was obtained from the originalregisters of the fish markets of Veniceand Chioggia that were availableon paper documents from 1945 to 1996,and in electronic spreadsheets from 1997. The data originally included information on landings from aquaculture and sea- and lagoon-fishery merged together.
